summary: 1963  was a common year starting on Tuesday of the Gregorian calendar.
full_text: 1963  was a common year starting on Tuesday  of the Gregorian calendar, the 1963rd year of the Common Era  and Anno Domini  designations, the 963rd year of the 2nd millennium, the 63rd year of the 20th century, and the 4th year of the 1960s decade.
